'''Sweetwater Township''' is a north western [[Township]], and one of the six townships of [[Clay County, North Carolina|Clay County]], [[North Carolina]], [[United States]]. The other five are Brasstown, Hayesville, Shooting Creek, Hiawassee, and Tusquittee.

